(1282, 158, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"25f56dbf\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2341b5ee\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2bb00d7\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/aira\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/07\\/pexels-rodnae-productions-7403007.jpg\",\"id\":231}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"45f7c15c\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><strong>What is ADHD?<\\/strong><\\/p><p>ADHD, or attention deficit hyperactivity disorder, is a common neurobehavioral medical condition that is typically diagnosed in childhood. It\'s characterized by inattention, hyperactivity, and impulsivity, all of which make it difficult for people to pay attention and manage their actions.<\\/p><p>ADHD is reported to be the most common mental health issue among children, with prevalence estimates ranging from 5 to 11%. Adults with ADHD are estimated to be less frequent, with just 2 to 5% of adults being diagnosed.<\\/p><p><strong>Causes of ADHD<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Although the actual causes of ADHD are unknown, experts believe that a number of factors are involved.<\\/p><ul><li>Genes and heredity<\\/li><li>Prenatal exposures<\\/li><li>Toxins in the environment<\\/li><li>Brain anatomy and function<\\/li><li>Head injuries<\\/li><\\/ul><p><strong>Treatment of ADHD<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Medication is the most common treatment for ADHD. Your doctor can adjust the prescription until the right therapeutic dose is found.<\\/p><p>Parent training provides emotional support as well as specific disciplining techniques that have been shown to reduce behavior problems.<\\/p><p>Cognitive-behavioral treatment may include social skills training. The therapy can be done in a group environment or one-on-one with a therapist, or an ADHD coach can teach social skills.<\\/p><p>Lifestyle Changes were exercise and eating a balanced diet can also assist with ADHD symptoms.<\\/p><p>Education, you can learn from websites, books, and podcasts. Consider attending classes held locally.<\\/p>\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Roboto Slab\",\"typography_font_weight\":\"400\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
