(1459, 175, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"16c8d327\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"20497422\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"54607ed\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/aira\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/07\\/992625.jpg\",\"id\":268}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"7b9c4d49\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><strong>What is Schizophrenia?<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Schizophrenia is a mental disorder that disrupts the normal functioning of the brain. This causes persistent issues with disordered thoughts and behaviors, as well as symptoms like hallucinations, delusions, and a lack of emotional expressiveness.<\\/p><p><strong>Causes of Schizophrenia<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Scientists are studying many possible factors that might cause a person with a genetic predisposition to develop schizophrenia.<\\/p><ul><li>Genetic factors<\\/li><li>Family relationships<\\/li><li>Alcohol and other drug use<\\/li><li>Stress<\\/li><\\/ul><p><strong>Treatment of Schizophrenia<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Psychotherapy can assist in the normalization of cognitive patterns. People with schizophrenia can also benefit from learning to cope with stress and recognizing early warning signs of illness.<\\/p><p>Training in social skills. This focuses on increasing communication and social connections, as well as improving daily activities participation.<\\/p><p>Therapy for the whole family. Families suffering from schizophrenia receive assistance and information through this program.<\\/p><p>Antipsychotic pharmaceuticals are the most commonly given antipsychotic medications, which are the cornerstone of schizophrenia treatment. They\'re considered to work by stimulating the dopamine neurotransmitter in the brain.<\\/p>\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"typography_font_family\":\"Roboto Slab\",\"typography_font_weight\":\"400\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
