(1868, 333, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"7b686d57\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"19f876e7\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"185ff7e\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/aira\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/07\\/pexels-dziana-hasanbekava-5480739.jpg\",\"id\":334}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"94125ab\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>\\u201cIf you are broken, you do not have to stay broken.\\u201d \\u2014 Selena Gomez<\\/p><p>\\u201cThis feeling will pass. The fear is real but the danger is not.\\u201d \\u2015 Cammie McGovern<\\/p><p>\\u201cBut no matter how much evil I see, I think it\\u2019s important for everyone to understand that there is much more light than darkness.\\u201d \\u2015 Robert Uttaro<\\/p><p>\\u201cTough times never last, but tough people do!\\u201d \\u2014 Robert Schuller<\\/p><p>\\u201cI keep moving ahead, as always, knowing deep down inside that I am a good person and that I am worthy of a good life.\\u201d \\u2015 Jonathan Harnisch<\\/p><p>\\u201cI would say what others have said: It gets better. One day, you\\u2019ll find your tribe. You just have to trust that people are out there waiting to love you and celebrate you for who you are. In the meantime, the reality is you might have to be your own tribe. You might have to be your own best friend. That\\u2019s not something they\\u2019re going to teach you in school. So start the work of loving yourself. \\u2014 Wentworth Miller<\\/p><p>\\u201cYou are the one thing in this world, above all other things, that you must never give up on. When I was in middle school, I was struggling with severe anxiety and depression, and the help and support I received from my family and a therapist saved my life. Asking for help is the first step. You are more precious to this world than you\\u2019ll ever know.\\u201d \\u2014 Lili Reinhart<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
