(1889, 338, '_elementor_data', '[{\"id\":\"6fa1dcfe\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"6ba42a82\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"b5abfac\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/aira\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2021\\/07\\/pexels-matthias-cooper-1062280.jpg\",\"id\":339}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"33186958\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>\\u201cYou don\\u2019t have to control your thoughts. You just have to stop letting them control you.\\u201d \\u2014 Dan Millman<\\/p><p>\\u201cTake your time healing, as long as you want. Nobody else knows what you\\u2019ve been through. How could they know how long it will take to heal you?\\u201d \\u2014 Abertoli<\\/p><p>\\u201cRecovery is not one and done. It is a lifelong journey that takes place one day, one step at a time.\\u201d \\u2014 Unknown<\\/p><p>\\u201cSelf-care is how you take your power back.\\u201d \\u2014 Lalah Delia<\\/p><p>\\u201cLet your story go. Allow yourself to be present with who you are right now.\\u201d \\u2013 Russ Kyle<\\/p><p>\\u201cMy dark days made me strong. Or maybe I already was strong, and they made me prove it.\\u201d \\u2014 Emery Lord<\\/p><p>\\u201cYou can\\u2019t control everything. Sometimes you just need to relax and have faith that things will work out. Let go a little and just let life happen.\\u201d \\u2014 Kody Keplinger<\\/p><p>\\u201cI am not afraid of storms for I am learning how to sail my ship.\\u201d \\u2014 Amy March, from Little Women<\\/p><p>\\u201cSometimes you climb out of bed in the morning and you think, I\\u2019m not going to make it, but you laugh inside \\u2014 remembering all the times you\\u2019ve felt that way.\\u201d \\u2014 Charles Bukowski<\\/p><p>\\u201cPromise me you\\u2019ll always remember \\u2014 you\\u2019re braver than you believe and stronger than you seem, and smarter than you think.\\u201d \\u2014 Christopher Robin from Winnie the Pooh<\\/p><p>\\u201cIf you\\u2019re going through hell, keep going.\\u201d \\u2014 Winston Churchill<\\/p><p>\\u201cIf you have been brutally broken but still have the courage to be gentle to other living beings, then you\\u2019re a badass with a heart of an angel.\\u201d \\u2014 Keanu Reeves<\\/p><p>\\u201cEmotional pain is not something that should be hidden away and never spoken about. There is truth in your pain, there is growth in your pain, but only if it\\u2019s first brought out into the open.\\u201d \\u2014 Steven Aitchison<\\/p><p>\\u201cYou, yourself, as much as anybody in the entire universe, deserve your love and affection.\\u201d \\u2014 Buddha<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
