ilable in Tagalog and English.</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Tel:893-7606, 893-7603</p>\n    63 917 800 1123\n63 2 893 7603\n63 922 893 8944\nEmail:<u>crisisline@i-manila.com.ph</u></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>', 'Get Help', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'get-help', '', '', '2021-07-08 11:10:23', '2021-07-08 11:10:23', '', 0, 'http://localhost/aira/?page_id=151', 0, 'page', '', 0),
