(264, 1, '2021-07-09 03:10:49', '2021-07-09 03:10:49', 'What is Depression?\r\n\r\nDepression (major depressive disorder) is a common and severe medical condition that has a negative impact on how you feel, think, and act.\r\n\r\nThe mood disorder may appear out of nowhere or after a loss or tragic tragedy, resulting in persistent emotions of despair, worthlessness, hopelessness, helplessness, negativity, or guilt. Depression also makes it difficult to concentrate, stay motivated, and perform other basic tasks.\r\n\r\nCauses of Depression\r\n\r\nThe minds of people who have depression look different from those who do not, according to research using brain-imaging technology such as Magnetic Resonance Imaging (MRI).\r\n\r\nAbuse in any kind, whether physical, sexual, or emotional, can lead to increased risk to depression later in life.\r\n\r\nDeath or a loss\r\n\r\nPersonal problems\r\n\r\nMajor events\r\n\r\nGenes\r\n\r\nCertain medications\r\n\r\nAge\r\n\r\nTreatment of Depression\r\n\r\nPsychotherapy is often referred to as talk therapy is a technique of assisting persons suffering from a wide range of mental illnesses and emotional problems.\r\n\r\nInterpersonal Therapy, the purpose of this form of treatment is to assist you in improving your relationship skills, such as communication and conflict resolution.\r\n\r\nCognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT) is a type of talk therapy that aims to help you change any negative thought or behavior patterns that are contributing to or worsening your depression.\r\n\r\nPsychodynamic therapy is a type of therapy were you will understand how your depression may be connected to prior events, unsolved conflicts, or unhealed wounds throughout these treatment sessions.\r\n\r\nBehavioral activation shows you how to develop goals and include more enjoyable activities into your daily routine.\r\n\r\nFamily or Couples Therapy. This type of therapy also include informing your family and friends about depression and how it affects you.', 'Depression', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '169-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-07-09 03:10:49', '2021-07-09 03:10:49', '', 169, 'http://localhost/aira/?p=264', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
