(297, 1, '2021-07-09 05:10:25', '2021-07-09 05:10:25', '<p>Doing things by yourself allows you to enjoy activities you love at your own pace and in your own way. You learn more about yourself and reflect on your experiences through solitary activities.</p><p><strong>Go to the movies alone</strong></p><p>When you watch a movie alone, you can concentrate entirely on the story and visual in front of you, rather than worrying about what your friends might think.</p><p><strong>Travel</strong></p><p>Traveling alone is a wonderful way to develop independence and confidence. It can also be a fun and enjoyable way to test your capabilities and develop new skills.</p><p><strong>Learn something new</strong></p><p>Instead of focusing on what other people want to accomplish, you might pursue something that fulfills your own passions.</p><p><strong>Volunteer</strong></p><p>Volunteering gives you the opportunity to practice and develop your social skills, since you are meeting regularly with a group of people with common interests.</p><p><strong>Take yourself out to dinner</strong></p><p>Taking yourself out for a delicious meal allows you to unwind and enjoy the experience in peace.</p>', 'Things to Do by Yourself', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'things-to-do-by-yourself__trashed', '', '', '2021-07-09 05:14:26', '2021-07-09 05:14:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/aira/?page_id=297', 0, 'page', '', 0),
