(360, 1, '2021-07-19 00:40:37', '2021-07-19 00:40:37', '<img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http://localhost/aira/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/pexels-cottonbro-4101164.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />															\n		Mental illness, often known as mental health disorders, involves a wide range of disorders that affect your emotions, thought, and behavior.\n<ul>\n 	<li>Depression</li>\n 	<li>Anxiety disorders</li>\n 	<li>Schizophrenia</li>\n 	<li>Eating disorders</li>\n 	<li>and addictive behaviors are all examples of mental disorders.</li>\n</ul>\nOur emotional, psychological, and social well-being are all part of our mental health. It has an impact on the way we think, feel, and act. It also influences how we deal with stress, interacts with others, and make decisions. Mental health is vital at all stages of life, including childhood, adolescence, and maturity.', 'Mental Health Disorders', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '125-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-07-19 00:40:37', '2021-07-19 00:40:37', '', 125, 'http://localhost/aira/?p=360', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
